{"tid":655030,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"15:45 [瘋人院逐個捉 / 鬼病院：靈異直播 / 昆池岩 곤지암 2018]","createTime":"2018-05-06T07:14:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-06T09:55:37.000Z","uid":34643,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"af3931cc5554b624611042a2f666e453c1717251","tid":655030,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T07:14:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://sites.simbla.com/871f3a54-3131-b616-e5df-b781f31a0a3a/iusee\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsites.simbla.com%2F871f3a54-3131-b616-e5df-b781f31a0a3a%2Fiusee&d=OQSvYg9voE7wDVd22Ueok9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=34dc7062\" target=\"_blank\">http://sites.simbla.com/871f3a54-3131-b616-e5df-b781f31a0a3a/iusee</a><br />\n<br />\n　　原名南營神經精神醫院的昆池岩精神病院，最早建立於20世紀60年代。在特殊的時代它曾經歷了無比的輝煌，然而更為人熟知的則是該醫院身上所發生的各類恐怖事件。現如今，早已廢棄的昆池岩醫院被CNN票選為全球七大恐怖之地之一，更由此吸引無數尋求刺激的青年男女來此探險。三個月前，兩名青少年來此探險，結果在直播中遭遇詭異事件，下落不明。此後，《恐怖世代》劇組在魏河俊的召集下，網羅了吳雅妍、樸智賢、夏洛特（文藝媛 飾）、李丞旭、樸成勛、劉帝允等人前往昆池岩，更試圖打開備受詛咒的401室。 <br />\n　　夜幕降臨，全球網友一道觀看這場恐怖盛宴&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://thumb22.jfcdns.com/thumb/up/2018-5/15254232176909651_460_380.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumb22.jfcdns.com%2Fthumb%2Fup%2F2018-5%2F15254232176909651_460_380.jpg&h=7b390386&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ccff8f5a53b46e0e9da08ffaf90d9c4a7af225e6","tid":655030,"uid":38820,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T07:15:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hk